[[Image:Friendly_city.jpg|right|600px]]
==Buildings==
Players use [[Resources (LoU)|resources]] to construct and improve buildings. Each building improves their Score, which determines their Ranking and can provide Titles. Each building also has a special function; a Town Hall, for instance, determines the maximum number of buildings that can exist within a city, provides workers to produce wood, and provides storage. Some are limited; each city can only have one Town Hall, Castle, or City Wall, for example.

